[Cases of rabies in unusual species, like this, originate most likely from a bite from the reservoir wildlife in the area. In eastern North America, raccoons are the reservoir species of terrestrial rabies. Raccoon rabies is caused by an antigenically distinct rabies virus variant. - Mod.PMB

